  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK204">
<l>maṟantum piṟaṉkēṭu cūḻaṟka cūḻi</l>
<l> ṉaṟañcūḻuñ cūḻntavaṉ kēṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though forgetfulness meditate not the ruin of another. Virtue will meditate the ruin of him who thus meditates.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
